PXASM.text:
%NOTE
            PXASM PANEXEC CNTL PROCEDURE.
 PANNAME=&1, GRP=&2, LOAD MODNAME=&3, COMPILE OPTIONS=&4, BRNCHLABEL=&5
 LKED OPTIONS=&6, SOURCE INDICATOR=&7 (%=PANVALET, *=NON-PANV)

&7BRANCH GT,4,NOLKED

%BRANCH GT,4,NOLKED
%BRANCH LE,4,&5

%NOLKED:
